title: RHOBH: Welcome to Jurassic Dark
description:
The "dark" controversy on Real Housewives of Beverly Hills crosses borders as the women head to Mexico for a much needed vacation from their three days of recovery from the last vacation. Plus, we say goodbye to the legendary Lois <3

This is a Crappens on Demand episode.  Check it out here:  https://www.patreon.com/posts/67575641
